						               													<description>Battle in league 5 vs 5 Arena matches, every-man-for-himself Battle Royale matches, or tour the world with your friends since 3 games come in 1 box with Bloodfist Champions. Bloodfist Champions allows for multiple ways to play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The original game, Bloodfist Champions, allows players to choose their fighting forces from 45 different teams, each with its own completely unique characters and style of play. Players battle through a league style setting, with each match awarding them experience points and gold for their team.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Bloodfist Champions: Battle Royale pits up to 30 players, each controlling one character, in a massive winner-take-all bout. It includes the same experience points and gold gains as the original, but focus is narrowed to what helps one player in the arena, rather than worrying about a whole team.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Bloodfist Champions: RPG is a tabletop roleplaying game in the world of Bloodfist, allowing players to experience the rich world as a group of traveling Bloodfist players, either as a team or as individual Battle Royale players (or both).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;All of this mayhem runs on a system of dice involving uniquely illustrated six-sided attack dice. You roll to attack your enemy, and, if successful, roll again to see if you hurt him. Any time you hit an opponent hard enough to hurt him in any way, you earn, 1, 2, 3, or 5 experience points for the player who performed it, and the same amount of points are scored toward victory for your team (or individual in Battle Royale).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
